{"tid":1813782,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[呢套超正] 輸給下半身欲望的「地上最強男人」，《彼得·格里爾的賢者時間》7月新番放送","createTime":"2020-01-06T13:45:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T14:13:48.000Z","uid":75050,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"df03f662e030d7307dc85f1eccb7c8c7aa8a2392","tid":1813782,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T13:45:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hkacger.com/archives/95871/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Farchives%2F95871%2F&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=56cf3769\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkacger.com/archives/95871/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/00-8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F00-8.jpg&h=08159487&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<strong><ins>輸給下半身欲望的「地上最強男人」，《彼得&middot;格里爾的賢者時間》7月新番放送</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n作者: ACGER編輯部 日期: 06/01/2020<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/01-37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F01-37.jpg&h=34bd6b5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2020年1月6日更新：《彼得&middot;格里爾的賢者時間》7月新番放送<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/%E5%BD%BC%E5%BE%97%C2%B7%E6%A0%BC%E9%87%8C%E7%88%BE%E7%9A%84%E8%B3%A2%E8%80%85%E6%99%82%E9%96%93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F%25E5%25BD%25BC%25E5%25BE%2597%25C2%25B7%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E9%2587%258C%25E7%2588%25BE%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%25B3%25A2%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%2596%2593.jpg&h=93e05e7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《彼得&middot;格里爾的賢者時間》這部漫畫只看簡介會以為是福利番，但實質上是一部歡樂搞笑番<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/%E5%BD%BC%E5%BE%97%C2%B7%E6%A0%BC%E9%87%8C%E7%88%BE%E7%9A%84%E8%B3%A2%E8%80%85%E6%99%82%E9%96%93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F%25E5%25BD%25BC%25E5%25BE%2597%25C2%25B7%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E9%2587%258C%25E7%2588%25BE%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%25B3%25A2%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%2596%2593.jpg&h=06b00eee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人類男主角的彼得&middot;格里爾在勝出武鬥會成為「地上最強的男人」，因此其最強遺傳因子就被異種族女性們盯上<br />\n<br />\n面對鬼族精靈族等異種族女性們的攻勢，已經有女友還要有婚約的男主角很快就把持不住，輸給了下半身的欲望&hellip;"},{"pid":"431074d72f6542b05f10ffde6c2d0a6cf2d682f9","tid":1813782,"uid":75050,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T13:53:45.000Z","msg":"呢套野漫畫笑撚到我，哥布林篇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QiPnKFt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQiPnKFt.jpg&h=bbcdb007&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z6wJt69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz6wJt69.jpg&h=96441208&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LpHMrTP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLpHMrTP.jpg&h=27918d7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hR3PpFt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhR3PpFt.jpg&h=eb3efe52&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D5RhyyQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD5RhyyQ.jpg&h=e27a0964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rvju87a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRvju87a.jpg&h=e9efad9b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a958b9646da10ee5b1c69d8c4b1412aeb63617a4","tid":1813782,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T22:41:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/he